name: Biofuel Oxite Dissolver
description: More efficient than theOxite Dissolver, this is used in tandem withOxygen Containersplaced into the oxidizer. The front slots of the deployable only acceptOxygen Containersand will automatically fill said containers fromOxiteplaced into the machine when supplied with Biofuel from aBiofuel Can. A fullBiofuel Canwill last three minutes and twenty seconds, producing 0.2 Liters of Oxygen every two seconds.
